description: Cirque du Sucré is serving all sorts of beautiful and delicious made-from-scratch sweets through the streets of Kansas City.Thought, care, and creativity go into the creation of their desserts, from the curation of the finest quality ingredients to the crafting of every unique design. This is why their Chunk Cookies, French Macarons, and eclectic selection of innovative ice creams are all feasts for your eyes that will surely delight you before you even take a bite. Their flavors range from Peaches & Cream to Sweet Corn Ice Cream, Carrot Cake to Sweet Potato, and everything in between. They’re all unique and all divine.For all this and much more amazingness, take your sweet tooth to quite a show, courtesy of Cirque du Sucré!
name: Cirque du Sucre
